{"tid":1355302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子涉上月向警署投擲汽油彈案　第5次申請保釋被拒","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:35:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5887d8def01f74d4d0c35ae0884e8ca52cac51","tid":1355302,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1469980_1_L_20190723173009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1469980_1_L_20190723173009.jpg&h=0493a65f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469980-20190723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469980-20190723.htm&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=11156d76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469980-20190723.htm&h=aeb07bd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469980-20190723.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n上月灣仔警察總部外及跑馬地分區警署外分別被投擲汽油彈，25歲被告莊鑫淼被控兩項縱火，第5次申請保釋被拒。<br />\n<br />\n莊鑫淼不服被裁判官下令還柙，在東區裁判法院第5次申請保釋。他申請期間提出「你叫邊個做我人事擔保我都請到，包括高院法官或者終院法官」，又說自己知名公司的行政總裁。裁判官拒絕保釋申請，又提醒控方被告曾提及三合會組織名稱，律政司可考慮著手處理。<br />\n<br />\n莊鑫淼質疑裁判官無有力證據裁定他有罪，表示會再申請覆核。"}]}